commit_message:
Add DictionaryField class to resource base

Add `DictionaryField` class capable of handling dictionaries in
resource body JSON.
This is necessary to be able to parse resources like Message
Registry:
"Messages": {
        "Success": {
            "Message": "Completed successfully",
            "Severity": "OK",
            [...]
        },
        "Failure": {
            "Message": "Failed",
            "Severity": "Critical",
            [...]
        }
}

